    <content>
      <section id="home">
        <h1>Online Game Coaching Ethos</h1>
        <p>At our online game coaching service, we provide expert coaching for three popular games: Hearthstone: Heroes of Warcraft, Legends of Runeterra, and Apex Legends (both Ranked and Normal modes).</p>
        <p>Our coaching sessions are personalized and tailored to each player's individual needs and goals. Whether you're looking to climb the ranks in Ranked Standard or enhance your skills in Normal Standard, our coaches will provide valuable insights, strategies, and feedback to help you level up your game.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="rules">
        <h2>📜 Rules</h2>
        <p>Ranked Mode: Lost Matches are charged 1.5 Gems/Coins less. Won Matches are charged normally. Extra Bonus from Won Matches is 2 Coins. Extra Bonus from Newly Acquired Ranked Mode Matches is 0.5 Gems.</p>
        <p>Normal Mode: Lost Matches are charged 1 Gem/Coin less. Won Matches are charged 0.5 Gem/Coin less. Extra Bonus from Won Normal Mode Matches is 1 Coin. Extra Bonus from Newly Acquired Normal Mode Matches is 0.5 Coins.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="prices">
        <h2>💰 Prices</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Gems: $2 or equivalent (charged in cash).</li>
          <li>Coins: $2 or equivalent (charged on-chain).</li>
          <li>Floor Price: 5 Gems or 5 Coins per match.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section id="times">
        <h2>⌚ Times</h2>
        <p>New Matches Availability: Matches can be performed during GMT 11 AM / 7 PM.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="social">
        <h2>🌐 Social</h2>
        <p>Required Decks: Decks for coaching sessions are published on our Social Outlets in <a href="https://linktr.ee">Linktr.ee</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </content>
    <script>
      <![CDATA[
      const burgerMenu = document.querySelector('.burger-menu');
      const mobileNav = document.querySelector('.mobile-nav');

      burgerMenu.addEventListener('click', function() {
        mobileNav.classList.toggle('mobile-active');
      });
